 <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Send your logo. <span class="text-gold-400">Stocked polos on hand.</span></h2>
 <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy-200">Talk to a real human who knows service-tech apparel.</p>
